high_descs: Head to the sink in front.
Pick up the apple in the sink.
Turn around and bring the apple to the microwave on the right.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Take the heated apple to the sink on the left.
Put the heated apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, then turn left to face the sink.
Take the apple from in the sink.
Turn around, go forward toward the door, then turn right to the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave.
Turn around, then go forward, then turn left to return to the sink.
Place the apple in the sink, in front of the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple in the sink.

high_descs: Go to the right and stand in front of the sink.
Take the apple out of the sink.
Turn around and stand in front of the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave, shut the door, open the door and take the apple out and shut the door.
Go to the right and stand in front of the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed apple in the sink.
